the first part of the EMIYA x Ishtar doujin is translated but the 2nd part is not

1st part: https://nhentai.net/g/207534/
2nd part: https://nhentai.net/g/233537/

I think Ishtar told them about her experience with EMIYA rather the master but i'm not sure

First off, an Emiya x Ishtar doujin? I thought it was just a legend. 

I may not know enough Japanese, but I am assuming Ishtar, Medb and Okita had their way with Master and they are basically helping her get in on that action.  If so, then it's nice to see harem girls get along.
